items.title: Giants to honor retiring Vogelsong on Sunday
items.summary: Ryan Vogelsong will officially retire from MLB as a member of the Giants, the club announced on Monday. The 40-year-old right-hander pitched 12 Major League seasons, including seven with San Francisco.
